    faq_title: FAQ – Frequently Asked Questions
    faq_description: We know the answers to frequently asked questions, if we haven\'t found the answer, just call us
    faq_q1: What should I do in case of a car breakdown on the road?
    faq_a1: Stop at a safe place, turn on the emergency alarm and put up an emergency stop sign, if possible. Call our manager, describe the problem and get help immediately
    faq_q2: How quickly can you arrive at the scene of the accident?
    faq_a2: We try to arrive as soon as possible. The time depends on the distance and the current workload of our tow trucks.
    faq_q3: How much does it cost to towing a car?
    faq_a3: The cost depends on various factors, including distance, type of car and type of service. To clarify the price, please call us.
    faq_q4: What documents will I need to towing the car
    faq_a4: Usually, you will need an identity card and registration documents for the car. The manager will inform you in detail when placing an order.
    
